        Added rolling capability.
        
        
        0.2.0 - 2015-12-31
        ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
        
        Dice statistics are now calculated using discrete distribution.  Contribution by @drhagen.
        
        0.1.3 - 2015-12-25
